        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(proxy): apply enhanced NO_PROXY matching to global undici dispatcher (fixes #95998)",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nFixes #95998.\n\nWhen `HTTPS_PROXY` is set in the environment, `ensureGlobalUndiciEnvProxyDispatcher()` installs a global undici `EnvHttpProxyAgent` that routes ALL HTTP requests through the proxy — including internal plugin requests that should bypass it via `NO_PROXY`. The built-in undici `EnvHttpProxyAgent` NO_PROXY matcher does not support leading-dot subdomain patterns, CIDR notation, or octet wildcards.\n\nOpenClaw already has an enhanced `matchesNoProxy()` function that handles these formats — but it was only used by provider HTTP helpers, NOT by the global dispatcher.\n\n## Changes Made\n\n1. **NO_PROXY-aware dispatcher wrapper**: Wraps the global EnvHttpProxyAgent so each dispatch checks OpenClaw's enhanced `matchesNoProxy()` before routing through the proxy.\n2. **All construction paths wrapped**: Applied in all three places that build an EnvHttpProxyAgent.\n\n## Evidence\n\n- **Unit tests:** `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/infra/net/proxy-env.test.ts` — 55/55 passed\n- **Dispatcher tests:** `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run src/infra/net/undici-global-dispatcher.test.ts` — 33/33 passed\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\n**Environment:** Linux, Node 24.13.1, OpenClaw latest\n\nEach test uses the actual `matchesNoProxy()` function that the PR wires into the global dispatcher:\n\n```\n✅ COS domain bypasses proxy with leading-dot (.myqcloud.com)\n   URL: https://cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/bucket\n   NO_PROXY: .myqcloud.com → matchesNoProxy = true\n\n✅ External domain routes through proxy (not bypassed)\n   URL: https://api.openai.com/v1/chat\n   NO_PROXY: .myqcloud.com → matchesNoProxy = false\n\n✅ CIDR range bypasses proxy\n   URL: http://100.64.0.3:8990\n   NO_PROXY: 100.64.0.0/10 → matchesNoProxy = true\n\n✅ localhost/127.0.0.1 bypass proxy\n   URL: http://localhost:8080/test\n   NO_PROXY: localhost,127.0.0.1 → matchesNoProxy = true\n```\n\n- [x] AI-assisted",
